item.description:
This weekend (Fri, Nov 5 and Sat, Nov 6) brings Gram National 2010 to Precinct, a two-night celebration of the music of Gram Parsons.

Below is the schedule from the Precinct website:

Fri, Nov 5
* 7:30 Jenee Halstead
* 8:00 Maynard & The Musties
* 8:50 Brian Molnar
* 9:00 Cosmic American Derelicts
* 10:30 Lydia Loveless
* 11:20 Twang Em High
* 12:10 Highway Ghosts
* 1:00 Jenee & Lindia

Sat, Nov 6
* 7:30 Jenee Hallstead
* 8:00 Rocking Horse Rodeo
* 8:50 Lynda Lucas
* 9:40 Jeff Byrd & Dirty Finch
* 10:30 The Molenes
* 11:20 25 Pearl
* 12:10 Loose Salute
* 1:00 Lynda Lucas / Derelicts

Facebook event: http://www.facebook.c...

Cost $10 per night or $15 for both nights (a great deal!)

See you there!
item.how_to_find_us: I'll email cell# to attendees or ask for meetup at the door
item.name: Gram National Nov 5-6 at Precinct
